        </item>
        <item>
            <title>警打击非法电动单车拘 19 人，联合外卖平台惩处违规外卖员</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/11/illegal-electric-vehicles-hk/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=illegal-electric-vehicles-hk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/11/illegal-electric-vehicles-hk/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 09:00:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
